⚖️ Legal Reality (this matters a lot)

You cannot just “redo movies.”

You need:

1. Rights / Licensing
	•	studios (Warner, Paramount, etc.)
	•	distributors
	•	estates (for certain films)

2. Actor Likeness Rights
	•	even for restoration, identity preservation matters
	•	voice changes especially sensitive

3. Clear Labeling
	•	“Restored” vs “Enhanced” vs “Adapted”

👉 This is the difference between:
	•	a real company
	•	and a shutdown letter

